      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700">
        <li>- Small business owners who need something custom without spending a fortune</li>
        <li>- Solo operators who want to automate repetitive admin</li>
        <li>- People with an idea who want a lean first version</li>
        <li>- Anyone paying for too many tools that still don't fit their workflow</li>
        <li>- Individuals who need a simple, tailored online solution</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/90 p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">A smarter alternative to expensive custom builds</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700">
        Traditional custom projects can be slow, costly, and harder than they need to be.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700">
        Tudouke uses AI to reduce build time and cost while keeping human judgment in the loop, so you can get a useful result faster, with less friction.
