      <%= link_to "Read FAQs", faq_path, class: "text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-800 hover:text-emerald-900" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="audit-form" class="mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl px-4 py-9 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-10">
  <div class="grid gap-8 rounded-3xl border border-cyan-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-cyan-50 to-emerald-50 p-6 shadow-sm lg:grid-cols-2 lg:p-10">
    <div>
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-cyan-700">Start here</p>
      <h2 class="mt-2 font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">Get your free project plan</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700">
        Tell me what you're trying to solve, and I'll help map out a practical digital solution you can actually use.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700">
        Fast to plan. Fair to price. Built with AI, guided by experience.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-5 rounded-2xl border border-cyan-100 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-50/80 via-white to-emerald-50/70 p-4 shadow-sm">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">No pressure, no confusing tech talk</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700">If you're not sure what you need yet, that's completely fine.</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-800">You can simply tell me:</p>
        <ul class="mt-2 space-y-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-500"></span>
            <span>what you're trying to do</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-500"></span>
            <span>what's currently frustrating</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-500"></span>
            <span>what you wish was easier</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-slate-500">No obligation. We only use your details to respond to this enquiry.</p>
